### Payment failure
POST http://localhost:8081/notify
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "messageCode": "PAY_FAIL_001",
    "messageDescription": "Payment failed for order #45678 due to insufficient funds",
    "source": "payment-gateway",
    "sourceID": "pg-instance-7"
}

